## Local Development

### Prerequisites

- Docker & Docker Compose
- Python 3.12+ with [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/)
{% if frontend_type == "react" -%}
- Node.js 22+
{% endif %}

### Getting Started

```bash
# Copy environment variables
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your values

# Start all services
make up

# View logs
make logs
```
